Name: Stories of Submission: Learn Your Place
About the game: Stories of Submission: Learn Your Place is the story of William, a man who thought he had life all figured out: beautiful wife, good job and a decent house. Then it all fell apart. Several years later, he still hasn't managed to pick up the pieces and move on. His life takes an unusual turn after his fateful encounter with Freyja, a no-nonsense Mistress looking for someone who can be shaped into the perfect servant. William is far from perfect, however. Can he confront his past and the mess he's made of his present for a shot at a new and unexpected future? Features: ■ A story centered around Femdom and featuring several fetishes. ■ 3 Sex scenes. ■ 3 Endings. ■ 6 Achievements. ■ Mistress Freyja. Trust us, she deserves to be called a feature ;)
